title: Gillette Venus Sensitive Women's Disposable Razors - Single Package of 3 Razors (Packaging May Vary)
description: Gillette Venus Sensitive Disposable Razor is a 3 bladed razor designed for women with sensitive skin. The razor features the SkinElixir lubrastrip and 3 curve-hugging blades for a smooth shave with up to 0% irritation. (US Consumer Study, Feb. 2018)
